We can select an optimization step by solving:

$$
\begin{aligned}
\arg \min_{\Delta w} \nabla_w \mathcal{L}^\top \Delta w + \frac{1}{2} \lambda \|\Delta w\|^2 &amp;= -\|\nabla_w \mathcal{L}\| / \lambda * \arg \max_{\|\Delta w\| = 1} \nabla_w \mathcal{L}^\top \Delta w \\
\text{step size} &amp;\quad \text{“duality map”}
\end{aligned}
$$

